title: Airbnb CEO Brian Chesky
itunes:title: Airbnb CEO Brian Chesky
description:
Brian Chesky, co-founder and CEO of Airbnb, talks about how Covid-19 changed travel forever, taking the company public and how he books his own stay at a property. He's on "The David Rubenstein Show: Peer-to-Peer Conversations." This was recorded Feb. 16.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
